    {
      "id": "gaklorr",
      "name": "Gaklorr",
      "title": "Gaklorr, the Ironfist Tyrant",
      "description": "Towering war-chief of the Broken Fang clan with a hulking green form, wielding a colossal spiked wooden mace. Slow but devastating attacks.",
      "lore": "In the shadowed depths of the Bloodcrag Highlands, where the earth trembles with the echoes of battle, Gaklorr reigns as an unrelenting force of destruction. Towering over his kin, his hulking green form is clad in the scars of a thousand conquests, each mark a testament to his brutal victories. Wielding a colossal spiked wooden mace, crafted from the bones of ancient warlords and ironwood felled by his own hand, he crushes anything foolish enough to stand in his path. Once a war-chief of the Broken Fang clan, Gaklorr defied the elders, claiming that only the strongest should rule. In his defiance, he challenged their might, and in a single night of bloodshed, he took their lives, their crowns, and their power. Now, he roams the land as a living legend, his slow, deliberate steps striking fear into all who hear them. Though his movements may be ponderous, a single swing of his mighty weapon can shatter steel and stone alike.",
      "type": ["Boss", "Orc"],
      "image": "gaklorr.gif",
